=Contextual Quote=

"I have called the motivating impulse for change in these “worlding cultures” ecority — a portmanteau word weaving together the ideas of ecology + integrity, with the whispered promise of the kind of wellbeing for our species that can only come from unity. Ecority is not a policy to be implemented; it’s a metabolic shift in human consciousness, a re-membering of our indivisible place within the web of life on Earth."

-Richard Hames [https://richarddavidhames.substack.com/p/towards-sufficiency-through-ecority]


